<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/131839-what-sort-of-ideas-did-clive-barker-get">What sort of ideas did Clive Barker get for his book The Thief of Always?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_131839'><a id="like_count_community_question_131839" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/131839?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">4 likes</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F32638.The_Thief_of_Always">like</a></span>

</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionTimestamp'>
<a href="/questions/131839-what-sort-of-ideas-did-clive-barker-get">7 years ago</a>
</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionPermalink'>
<a href="/questions/131839-what-sort-of-ideas-did-clive-barker-get">Add your answer</a>
